 1994-18491994-11-010IA&ND,  ,  ,  , 
PrecisConfirmation of a second "SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT" between the Crown, the Province of Ontario and THE GARDEN RIVER FIRST NATION AND BAND OF INDIANS whereby a total of 3,521 hectares of land situate in the Townships of Chesley and Anderson will be set apart as an addition to Garden River Indian Reserve No. 14, and the Province will pay compensation for the transfer of 1,107 hectares of land as well as up to 212 more hectares for the construction of a four-lane highway. (PHASE II)
